he <strong>2018 Survey of Employee Earnings and Hours (EEH)<\/strong> which was conducted with respect to the last pay period on or before 18 May 2018.<\/p>\n<p>The EEH survey is conducted every two years and provides detailed statistics on the composition and distribution of employee earnings, hours paid for and the methods used to set employees&#8217; pay.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Source<\/strong>: <a href=\"http:\/\/www.abs.gov.au\/ausstats\/abs@.nsf\/mf\/6306.0?OpenDocument\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">http:\/\/www.abs.gov.au\/ausstats\/abs@.nsf\/mf\/6306.0?OpenDocument<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Based on this information, the <strong>Top 10\u00a0highest-earning occupations<\/strong> are:<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/top10.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-35530\" src=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/top10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1144\" height=\"741\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/top10.jpg 1144w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/top10-300x194.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/top10-768x497.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/top10-1024x663.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1144px) 100vw, 1144px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>This information has already been incorporated on <strong>Anzscosearch<\/strong> when <a href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/search\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">searching by ANZSCO<\/a> code.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/averageweek.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-35531\" src=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/averageweek.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1166\" height=\"445\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.anzscosearch.com\/wp-content